// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3946 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02bd6635-d77b-5448-94fe-57a17ab32ca7

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
